<C>__{surgeon}
<D>__{you're an organ donor!}
<C>__{organ donor}
<D>__{am i dead?!?}
<C>__{surgeon}
<D>__{the chute didn't open. we kind of assumed }
<C>__{organ donor}
<D>__{i need this body. just for a few minutes. i will bring it back, okay?}
<A>__{the organ donor grabs a lab coat from a nearby rack and races out. (and since stu is temporarily occupying the donor's body, we will henceforth refer to him as o.d. stu.)}
